latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Located in Park Street, the place provides amazing party vibes. Been there with my friends for an evening bash. Great ambience with live DJ. A perfect place to chill out with friends. The ambiance will surely give you party vibes. The management of the pub was well maintained and the staffs were courteous. The food was so tasty and quality was good enough. Coming to the food section , We ordered :
Food - Cajun fried Chicken, Prawn Tempura , Chicken Salami Pizza, Mexican Sizzler ;
Drinks - Thai High 2.0, Cool Babe, Pillow fight, Kingfisher Ultra;
Hookah - blueberry spring water. 
Hookah was amazing. and the cocktails were just wow in taste. Overall we were happy with the ambience and the super delicious foods. Carpe Diem perfectly gives justice to it's name as it is the perfect place to Seize the Day. Highly recommend.
